data.text:
Mid-city Community Advocacy Network, a Nonprofit Public Benefit Corporation, is a business entity located in San Diego, CA. Officially filed on February 4, 2019, this corporation is recognized under the document number 4240817. Governed by the California Secretary of State, the corporation maintains an active filing status.

The principal address of the corporation is located at 4305 University Avenue, 550, San Diego, CA 92105 and mailing address is at 4305 University Ave, Ste. 550, San Diego, CA 92105, serving as the central hub for its business operations and correspondence.

Ensuring the legal and official compliance of the corporation, Diana Rodriguez Ross acts as the registered agent. He operates from 4305 University Avenue Suite 550, San Diego, CA 92105.
